{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2053586, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 400705, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "不道歉至少承认个错误？一帮听得风就是雨的家伙", "timestamp": 1626102300, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2053610, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 400705, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "中国为啥无聊到和塔利班交朋友？", "timestamp": 1626102540, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2053612, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 400705, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "金三胖子，塔利班，普大帝，中国交一个民主点的朋友成不成啊？", "timestamp": 1626102564, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2053630, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 400705, "reply_to": 2053612, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 中国是现有民主秩序的挑战者", "timestamp": 1626102701, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2053647, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 400705, "reply_to": 2053612, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 民主国家是美国的朋友", "timestamp": 1626102848, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2053651, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 400705, "reply_to": 2053647, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 因为民主本身由美帝定义", "timestamp": 1626102883, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2053676, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 400705, "reply_to": 2053612, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 塔利班不是民主政权，但塔利班的上台确实反映了阿富汗人民的意志，有问题？", "timestamp": 1626103044, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2053689, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 400705, "reply_to": 2053612, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 成啊，塞尔维亚，匈牙利，菲律宾，巴基斯坦哪个不是民主的？你自己戳瞎了双眼不要找我抱怨啊", "timestamp": 1626103102, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2053704, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 400705, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "老胡说塔利班现在视美国为仇敌，然而实际上，塔利班发布的声明并没有表达这层意思。", "timestamp": 1626103249, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2053711, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 400705, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "#399813 ", "timestamp": 1626103301, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2053714, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 400705, "reply_to": 2053704, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 老胡并没有说他的这个“仇敌”的判断是从塔利班的发言得出的", "timestamp": 1626103318, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2053728, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 400705, "reply_to": 2053711, "tag": null, "text": "我觉得塔利班实际上是对所有主权国家展示善意，与恐怖组织划清界限，但老胡这一褒一贬真没必要", "timestamp": 1626103456, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2053745, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 400705, "reply_to": 2053728, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 你这种说法我是同意的，他就习惯性的叼个盘，翼赞一番罢了，但有些人阴阳的角度实在太离谱了", "timestamp": 1626103533, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2054187, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 400705, "reply_to": 2053676, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 只有民主政权才谈得上反不反映人民意志", "timestamp": 1626106590, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2054194, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 400705, "reply_to": 2053676, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 秦始皇统一中国和人民意志半毛钱关系没有，一姓之天下罢了", "timestamp": 1626106626, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2054257, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 400705, "reply_to": 2054187, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 不对，内战状态是绝对的民主", "timestamp": 1626106902, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2054271, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 400705, "reply_to": 2054194, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 那请你解释下，美国人剿匪剿了十年，最后傀儡被人反杀是怎么回事。我认为是人民的意志，你有其他结论请举证", "timestamp": 1626106980, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2054280, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 400705, "reply_to": 2054187, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 中国内战也反映人民意志，虽然双方都不民主", "timestamp": 1626107041, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2054281, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 400705, "reply_to": 2054257, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 人民支持不等于政权能代表人民的意志和利益，可能是因为旧的更烂", "timestamp": 1626107042, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2054328, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 400705, "reply_to": 2054281, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 是，至少塔利班相对符合人民意志，得国方式是正的。剩下的并不是我们需要关心的范畴，毕竟无论中美，结交的专制国家都不在少数", "timestamp": 1626107345, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2054355, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 400705, "reply_to": 2054281, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 我说的绝对民主的意思是：在政权二选一的意义上，阿富汗内战反应的结果是不容置疑的", "timestamp": 1626107560, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2054389, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 400705, "reply_to": 2054281, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 另外，我不认为有能“完全代表人民利益”的政权，你说的完全是理想化的伪命题", "timestamp": 1626107852, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2054396, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 400705, "reply_to": 2054281, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 或者说，内战和二选一的全民公投在道德上有相同效力", "timestamp": 1626107906, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2054426, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 400705, "reply_to": 2054396, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 民主国家通过不断的公投，民众可以持续监督政府，而革命则是几百年一次的事情，这几百年之间民众都只能期盼统治者大发慈悲", "timestamp": 1626108296, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2054431, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 400705, "reply_to": 2054426, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 你说的对，但阿富汗刚刚完成公投时间不久，你就来质疑塔利班合法性，不合适吧", "timestamp": 1626108341, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2054445, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 400705, "reply_to": 2054426, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 还有，你所说的不断公投是理想化情况，现实是中东极少有成熟的民主政权，这说明你的推论和中东的现实有内在矛盾。我看还是革命靠谱一点", "timestamp": 1626108585, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 1, "pid": 400705, "reply": 26, "tag": "政治相关", "text": "所以呢，塔利班的事情已经有真相了，他们确实说过不会让别人利用阿富汗反华之类的话。阴阳怪气的不来给胡叼盘道个歉？至少这次人家确实没说错啊", "timestamp": 1626102257, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1626108583, "url": "", "vote": {}}}